## CSS Architecture (Modular)

### Current Status
- **Variables & Base:** ✅ Complete (`variables.css`, `base.css`)
- **Components:** ⚠️ Partial - Only `navigation.css` exists, others are planned
- **Pages:** ⚠️ Not started - Directories exist but files not created
- **Utils:** ⚠️ Not started - Directories exist but files not created
- **Legacy:** `styles.css` still exists and contains all styles (needs migration)

**Migration Status:** CSS migration is in progress. Most styles are still in the legacy `styles.css` file. See `MIGRATION_GUIDE.md` for migration details.

### Main Entry Point
- **`css/main.css`** - Main CSS file that imports all modules
  - **DO NOT edit this file directly** - It only contains @import statements
  - All CSS should be in component/module files
  - **Note:** Currently imports many files that don't exist yet (these will be created during migration)

